eNarrative.eNarrative.01: Patient and his wife were enjoying some "R&R" by camping since Monday. Patient awoke to chest pain. After about an hour, patient's wife alerted AR Game & Fish officer on site. Game & Fish officer immediately called 911. Local FD responded while awaiting our arrival. Our evaluation indicated STEMI. We transported to PCI center with pre-arrival notification and arranged direct admit to cath lab.
